{
  "dialogueLines":
  [
    {
      "id": "intro_1",
      "illustration": "placeholder1",
      "portrait": "elias",
      "bodyText": "1...",
      "nameText": "Elias"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "illustration": "placeholder1",
      "portrait": "elias",
      "bodyText": "2...",
      "nameText": "Elias"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "illustration": "placeholder1",
      "portrait": "elias",
      "bodyText": "...3!",
      "nameText": "Elias"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "illustration": "placeholder1",
      "portrait": "elias",
      "bodyText": "Lola, why exactly do we have to do this every year?",
      "nameText": "Elias"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_5",
      "illustration": "placeholder2",
      "portrait": "lola_isang",
      "bodyText": "Ah, apo. Could you pass me that <i>anito book</i> on the table?",
      "nameText": "Lola Isang"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_6",
      "illustration": "placeholder2",
      "portrait": "elias",
      "bodyText": "This one Lola? It..",
      "nameText": "Elias"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_7",
      "illustration": "placeholder2",
      "portrait": "elias",
      "bodyText": "It can hardly pass as a book at this point po.",
      "nameText": "Elias"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_8",
      "illustration": "placeholder2",
      "portrait": "lola_isang",
      "bodyText": "That's called an anito book, gifted to us by the spirits.",
      "nameText": "Lola Isang"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_9",
      "illustration": "placeholder2",
      "portrait": "lola_isang",
      "bodyText": "It has been passed down thr—!",
      "nameText": "Lola Isang"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_10",
      "illustration": "placeholder2",
      "portrait": "elias",
      "bodyText": "Are spirits usually this stingy?",
      "nameText": "Elias"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_11",
      "illustration": "placeholder2",
      "portrait": "lola_isang",
      "bodyText": "N-No Elias, do not—",
      "nameText": "Lola Isang"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_12",
      "illustration": "placeholder2",
      "portrait": "lola_isang",
      "bodyText": "...",
      "nameText": "Lola Isang"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_13",
      "illustration": "placeholder2",
      "portrait": "elias",
      "bodyText": "Lola! Why is this happening?!",
      "nameText": "Elias"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_14",
      "illustration": "placeholder2",
      "portrait": "lola_isang",
      "bodyText": "Torn pages...",
      "nameText": "Lola Isang"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_15",
      "illustration": "placeholder2",
      "portrait": "lola_isang",
      "bodyText": "Iho! Take the Anito book with you and get in the house!",
      "nameText": "Lola Isang"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_16",
      "illustration": "placeholder2",
      "portrait": "elias",
      "bodyText": "Wha— but what about you?!",
      "nameText": "Elias"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_17",
      "illustration": "",
      "portrait": "lola_isang",
      "bodyText": "This isn't something we can stop together.",
      "nameText": "Lola Isang"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_18",
      "illustration": "",
      "portrait": "lola_isang",
      "bodyText": "Once things have subsided, an ally should be residing in the Balete trees..",
      "nameText": "Lola Isang"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_19",
      "illustration": "",
      "portrait": "lola_isang",
      "bodyText": "Now, go! Your Lola Isang will be looking after you!",
      "nameText": "Lola Isang"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_20",
      "illustration": "",
      "portrait": "lola_isang",
      "bodyText": "<i>I leave the rest to you Elias, go and be a babaylan...</i>",
      "nameText": "Lola Isang"
    }
  ]
}